## Quickstart


## Number of LLM calls
- 2 LLM calls per cluster


## Instructions for use
Assume df has columns: 
- content_str
- embedding_vector

Gets additional columns after applying .label(df, data_description)
- cluster_id
- topic_label
- membership_score
- outlier_score
- silhouette_score
- reduced_vector

